      "text": "그래서 돈을 에디션이 벌고 테슬라가 못 벌었던 거구나"
    },
    {
      "start": 562.5,
      "end": 563.12,
      "text": "Poor Tesla"
    },
    {
      "start": 563.12,
      "end": 563.56,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 563.56,
      "end": 568.52,
      "text": "Men claim to have their heads full of sonnets and symphonies"
    },
    {
      "start": 568.52,
      "end": 570.7,
      "text": "But their only problem seems to be"
    },
    {
      "start": 570.7,
      "end": 573.1,
      "text": "They can't quite write it down"
    },
    {
      "start": 573.1,
      "end": 573.56,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 573.56,
      "end": 575.16,
      "text": "Edison이 한 말이거든요"
    },
    {
      "start": 575.16,
      "end": 576.16,
      "text": "지적이에요"
    },
    {
      "start": 576.16,
      "end": 576.46,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 576.46,
      "end": 577.36,
      "text": "아주 좋은 지적이네요"
    },
    {
      "start": 577.36,
      "end": 578.58,
      "text": "Men"
    },
    {
      "start": 578.58,
      "end": 579.52,
      "text": "사람들은"
    },
    {
      "start": 579.52,
      "end": 581.36,
      "text": "Claim to 주장하지"
    },
    {
      "start": 581.36,
      "end": 584.94,
      "text": "Have their heads full of sonnets and symphonies"
    },
    {
      "start": 584.94,
      "end": 585.2,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 585.2,
      "end": 585.54,
      "text": "Sonnet"
    },
    {
      "start": 585.54,
      "end": 586.34,
      "text": "Do you know a sonnet?"
    },
    {
      "start": 587.5,
      "end": 588.1,
      "text": "14행시?"
    },
    {
      "start": 588.32,
      "end": 589.52,
      "text": "시의 일종이잖아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 589.52,
      "end": 591.12,
      "text": "Is that popular in Korea too?"
    },
    {
      "start": 591.36,
      "end": 592.8,
      "text": "The 14-line poem?"
    },
    {
      "start": 592.8,
      "end": 594.04,
      "text": "I don't think so"
    },
    {
      "start": 594.04,
      "end": 595.12,
      "text": "When I was in high school"
    },
    {
      "start": 595.12,
      "end": 596.08,
      "text": "American high schools"
    },
    {
      "start": 596.08,
      "end": 597.16,
      "text": "And middle schools"
    },
    {
      "start": 597.16,
      "end": 598.6,
      "text": "I think it was middle school"
    },
    {
      "start": 598.6,
      "end": 600.18,
      "text": "They make you write sonnets"
    },
    {
      "start": 600.18,
      "end": 600.64,
      "text": "Wow"
    },
    {
      "start": 600.64,
      "end": 602.08,
      "text": "And make a whole book of poetry"
    },
    {
      "start": 602.08,
      "end": 602.54,
      "text": "Wow"
    },
    {
      "start": 602.54,
      "end": 603.64,
      "text": "With 14 lines"
    },
    {
      "start": 603.64,
      "end": 604.04,
      "text": "Wow"
    },
    {
      "start": 604.04,
      "end": 604.96,
      "text": "And they have to rhyme"
    },
    {
      "start": 604.96,
      "end": 606.22,
      "text": "A specific way"
    },
    {
      "start": 606.22,
      "end": 607.2,
      "text": "너무 귀엽겠다"
    },
    {
      "start": 607.2,
      "end": 608.74,
      "text": "It was very difficult"
    },
    {
      "start": 608.74,
      "end": 609.54,
      "text": "어려웠어요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 609.56,
      "end": 609.74,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 609.74,
      "end": 611.3,
      "text": "I like to make raps"
    },
    {
      "start": 611.3,
      "end": 612.8,
      "text": "But freestyle rap"
    },
    {
      "start": 613.5,
      "end": 614.34,
      "text": "한번 들려주세요"
    },
    {
      "start": 614.34,
      "end": 614.7,
      "text": "Right now"
    },
    {
      "start": 614.7,
      "end": 615.3,
      "text": "기억나는 거"
    },
    {
      "start": 615.3,
      "end": 615.86,
      "text": "Hey"
    },
    {
      "start": 615.86,
      "end": 617.8,
      "text": "My name is Chris with the Gap"
    },
    {
      "start": 617.8,
      "end": 618.24,
      "text": "But okay"
    },
    {
      "start": 618.24,
      "end": 619.64,
      "text": "Oh my gosh"
    },
    {
      "start": 619.64,
      "end": 620.56,
      "text": "너무 재밌다"
    },
    {
      "start": 620.56,
      "end": 621.76,
      "text": "지금 민망하니까"
    },
    {
      "start": 621.76,
      "end": 622.64,
      "text": "넘어가요"
    },
    {
      "start": 622.64,
      "end": 623.14,
      "text": "Okay"
    },
    {
      "start": 623.14,
      "end": 623.76,
      "text": "나중에"
    },
    {
      "start": 623.76,
      "end": 624.28,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 624.28,
      "end": 626.6,
      "text": "사람들은 자기 머릿속에"
    },
    {
      "start": 626.6,
      "end": 628.68,
      "text": "시하고 교양곡"
    },
    {
      "start": 628.68,
      "end": 630.66,
      "text": "symphonies으로 가득 차있다라고"
    },
    {
      "start": 630.66,
      "end": 631.38,
      "text": "주장하죠"
    },
    {
      "start": 631.38,
      "end": 633.92,
      "text": "But their only problem"
    },
    {
      "start": 633.92,
      "end": 636.06,
      "text": "하지만 그들의 문제라는 게"
    },
    {
      "start": 636.06,
      "end": 636.76,
      "text": "뭐가 있냐면"
    },
    {
      "start": 636.76,
      "end": 637.76,
      "text": "Seems to be"
    },
    {
      "start": 637.76,
      "end": 639.72,
      "text": "they can't quite write it down"
    },
    {
      "start": 639.72,
      "end": 641.88,
      "text": "써내질 못한다라는 겁니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 641.88,
      "end": 643.08,
      "text": "라는 거예요"
    },
    {
      "start": 643.08,
      "end": 645.2,
      "text": "So what good is an idea"
    },
    {
      "start": 645.2,
      "end": 646.78,
      "text": "if you can't write it down"
    },
    {
      "start": 646.78,
      "end": 648.4,
      "text": "and present it to others"
    },
    {
      "start": 648.4,
      "end": 648.88,
      "text": "그렇죠"
    },
    {
      "start": 648.88,
      "end": 650.66,
      "text": "to make into reality"
    },
    {
      "start": 650.66,
      "end": 651.12,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 651.12,
      "end": 653.44,
      "text": "많은 분들이 동의하시는 분들도"
    },
    {
      "start": 653.44,
      "end": 654.18,
      "text": "계실 것 같은데"
    },
    {
      "start": 654.18,
      "end": 655.0,
      "text": "그래요"
    },
    {
      "start": 655.0,
      "end": 656.84,
      "text": "머릿속에는 여러가지 생각이 있어도"
    },
    {
      "start": 656.84,
      "end": 658.06,
      "text": "써내지 못한다면"
    },
    {
      "start": 658.06,
      "end": 659.68,
      "text": "아 그래요"
    },
    {
      "start": 659.68,
      "end": 661.3,
      "text": "그렇게 그렇게 좋은 방법은"
    },
    {
      "start": 661.3,
      "end": 661.9,
      "text": "아닌 것 같습니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 661.9,
      "end": 662.46,
      "text": "I'm a genius"
    },
    {
      "start": 662.46,
      "end": 663.2,
      "text": "I could do that"
    },
    {
      "start": 663.2,
      "end": 663.92,
      "text": "I could do that"
    },
    {
      "start": 663.92,
      "end": 664.64,
      "text": "누가 믿겠어요"
    },
    {
      "start": 664.64,
      "end": 665.68,
      "text": "It's all in my head"
    },
    {
      "start": 665.68,
      "end": 666.06,
      "text": "Right"
    },
    {
      "start": 666.06,
      "end": 666.62,
      "text": "믿어봐"
