    {
      "start": 666.62,
      "end": 667.1,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 667.1,
      "end": 668.44,
      "text": "I understand why"
    },
    {
      "start": 668.44,
      "end": 670.66,
      "text": "Edison is worried"
    },
    {
      "start": 670.66,
      "end": 672.46,
      "text": "about Tesla right now"
    },
    {
      "start": 672.46,
      "end": 672.74,
      "text": "Right"
    },
    {
      "start": 672.74,
      "end": 673.42,
      "text": "당연한 거죠"
    },
    {
      "start": 673.42,
      "end": 675.04,
      "text": "자 이 내용 떠올리시고"
    },
    {
      "start": 675.04,
      "end": 676.62,
      "text": "마지막으로 한 번 더 들어보겠습니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 676.62,
      "end": 679.04,
      "text": "You are not thinking long term"
    },
    {
      "start": 679.04,
      "end": 681.26,
      "text": "This technology is within your grasp"
    },
    {
      "start": 681.26,
      "end": 682.72,
      "text": "I can build you an efficient motor"
    },
    {
      "start": 682.72,
      "end": 683.98,
      "text": "Have you tried it?"
    },
    {
      "start": 684.76,
      "end": 685.02,
      "text": "No"
    },
    {
      "start": 685.02,
      "end": 686.48,
      "text": "Look in my head"
    },
    {
      "start": 686.48,
      "end": 687.48,
      "text": "It is nearly completed"
    },
    {
      "start": 687.48,
      "end": 688.64,
      "text": "My plane to have their heads"
    },
    {
      "start": 688.64,
      "end": 689.78,
      "text": "full of sonnets and symphonies"
    },
    {
      "start": 689.78,
      "end": 691.16,
      "text": "But their only problem seems to be"
    },
    {
      "start": 691.16,
      "end": 692.94,
      "text": "they can't quite write it down"
    },
    {
      "start": 692.94,
      "end": 694.29,
      "text": "네"
    },
    {
      "start": 694.29,
      "end": 696.99,
      "text": "크리스의 연기력이 좋다라고"
    },
    {
      "start": 696.99,
      "end": 698.79,
      "text": "여기저기서 소문이 들리고 있어요"
    },
    {
      "start": 698.79,
      "end": 701.21,
      "text": "7545님께서도"
    },
    {
      "start": 701.21,
      "end": 702.83,
